CERTIFICATE OF CONCURRENCE
This is to certify that Imperial Valley Solar 1, LLC ("IVS-1") assents and concurs in the rate schedule described below, which CSOLAR IV South, LLC ("CSOLAR") has filed, and hereby files this certificate of concurrence in lieu of the filing of the rate schedule specified.
CSOLAR's Tariff Record Adopted by Reference: CSOLAR's Rate Schedule FERC No. 1
Description of Tariff Record Adopted by Reference: Co-Tenancy and Shared Use Agreement among CSOLAR, IVS-1, and Imperial Valley Solar, LLC and Amendment No. 1 thereto
Imperial Valley Solar 1, LLC By its counsel,
/s/ Adam Wenner Adam Wenner Orrick, Herrington & Sutcliffe LLP 1152 15th Street, N.W. Washington, D.C. 20005
Dated: May 29, 2013
